# Ignore everything by default
*

# Allow only specific directories (and their contents)
!README.md
!data_processing/
!data_processing/**
!lfmc_model/
!lfmc_model/**

# Still ignore unwanted stuff inside allowed dirs
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/.DS_Store
**/._.DS_Store
**/*.out
**/*.err
**/*.log
**/logs/
**/testing/
**/old/
!data_processing/daymet/old/
